Dolores Dwyer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dolores_Dwyer 0 Dolores Dwyer (married name Duffy; December 25, 1934 – October 29, 2011) was an American sprinter. She competed in the Women's 200 metres event at the 1952 Summer Olympics. In her later life, she became an actress, which included a role in the television show Sex and the City.
